This document explains how to build the Linux vendor
library for the HBA API.

##
# libhbalinux
##############

DEPENDENCIES

* HBA API Wrapper Library

* autoconf
* autotools
* sysconftool
* automake
* libtool
* libpciaccess-devel

PROCESS

1) Bootstrap, configure, make and make install
   # ./bootstrap.sh
   # rpm --eval "%configure" | sh
   # make
   # make install
